1. *Ranjen* vojnik se vraća kući. (A *wounded* soldier is returning home.)
2. Videla sam *ranjenog* psa na ulici. (I saw a *wounded* dog on the street.)
3. Doktori pokušavaju da spase *ranjenog* pacijenta. (Doctors are trying to save a *wounded* patient.)
4. *Ranjeni* vojnik je primljen u bolnicu. (The *wounded* soldier was admitted to the hospital.)
5. Nekoliko *ranjenih* ljudi je bilo na mestu nesreće. (Several *wounded* people were at the scene of the accident.)
6. *Ranjeni* su prevezeni helikopterom do bolnice. (The *wounded* were transported by helicopter to the hospital.)
7. Oporavak od *ranjenih* nogu je dug i težak proces. (Recovery from *wounded* legs is a long and difficult process.)
8. Među *ranjenima* su bili i civili. (Among the *wounded* were civilians.)
9. *Ranjeni* vojnik se polako oporavlja. (The *wounded* soldier is slowly recovering.)
10. Policija traga za napadačem koji je *ranio* prolaznika. (The police are searching for the attacker who *shot* a passerby.)